==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hewn
<hw>Hewn</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Felled, cut,
or shaped as with an ax; roughly squared; <as>as, a house built of
<ex>hewn</ex> logs</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Roughly dressed as with a hammer; <as>as,
<ex>hewn</ex> stone</as>.</def></p>

<p><ent>Hexa</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Hex-</ent>⟦br⟧
